OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter early morning cloud
OL,6,Fclears, another bright and sunny day
OL,7,Fwill follow for all. Winds lighter
OL,8,Fthan Wednesday allowing temperatures
OL,9,Fto climb further. UV levels will also
OL,10,Fbe high in the sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear night to start with
OL,13,Flight winds, but patchy cloud
OL,14,Fdeveloping from the east. Some mist
OL,15,Fand fog forming in prone clear spots,
OL,16,Fwith a grass frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
