OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny mist, fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fwill clear quickly after the sunrises.
OL,7,FAnother bright and sunny day expected
OL,8,Fwith temperatures slightly higher than
OL,9,FThursday.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Fwarm and sunny into the weekend with
OL,13,Flight winds. Likely to be more cloud
OL,14,Fon Sunday which will allow
OL,15,Ftemperatures to dip slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
